    "title": {
      "rendered": "LinkedIn Launches Volunteer Marketplace for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-15419\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Volunteering-Is-Good-for-Your-Career-LinkedIn-Nonprofits-final.jpg?w=320&amp;ssl=1 320w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>To help nonprofits recruit qualified volunteers and to assist individuals eager to volunteer with nonprofits, LinkedIn has launched a <a href=\"http://volunteer.linkedin.com/index.html\">Volunteer Marketplace</a>\u00a0where nonprofits can post volunteer opportunities and LinkedIn members can search for volunteer opportunities in their local communities. According to <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/lifg\">LinkedIn for Good</a>,\u00a082% of surveyed LinkedIn members have communicated that they want volunteer their time and skills and thus far more than 600,000 LinkedIn members have added their <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/edit-volunteering-combined?trk=Vol_LIFG_Prof_Exp\">Volunteer Experience &amp; Causes</a> to their LinkedIn profiles.</p>\n<p>The service is not free for nonprofits, but it is offered at a discounted rate of 90 percent off LinkedIn&#8217;s standard rate for job postings, thus $19.50 for a 30-day volunteer posting. To begin, your nonprofit must first claim and set up your <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2013/07/14/ten-must-follow-nonprofits-on-linkedin/\">LinkedIn Company Page</a>\u00a0and then visit <a href=\"http://nonprofit.linkedin.com/index.html\">LinkedIn for Nonprofits</a>\u00a0to post your volunteer opportunities:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofit.linkedin.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15404\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"linkedin for nonprofits\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/linkedin-for-nonprofits.png?resize=600%2C289\" width=\"600\" height=\"289\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/linkedin-for-nonprofits.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/linkedin-for-nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C144&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
